                                                                th.sorting(data-hide='phone,tablet', tabindex='0', aria-controls='datatable_col_reorder', rowspan='1', colspan='1', aria-label='Zip: activate to sort column ascending', style='width: 80px;') 开课学院
                                                                th.sorting(data-hide='phone,tablet', tabindex='0', aria-controls='datatable_col_reorder', rowspan='1', colspan='1', aria-label='City: activate to sort column ascending', style='width: 80px;') 课程名称
